form action="/your-menu" method="post"
  .row
    .col-xs-12
      p
        strong
          ' Build an action menu for
          a href="http://contrast.co/launch-center-pro/" Launch Center Pro
          ' that can be activated by a bookmarklet in Safari.
      p
      ' Add up to six actions to your menu. Choose an icon for each action. Click the button at the bottom, and BAM, your menu bookmarklet will appear along with instructions for how to install it.
      p
      ' You'll need to install Launch Center Pro (for
      a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/launch-center-pro/id532016360?mt=8&at=11lsTn" iPhone
      '  or
      a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/launch-center-pro-for-ipad/id799664902?mt=8&at=11lsTn" iPad
      '), and it would probably help to have a copy of Drafts (for
      a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/drafts/id502385074?mt=8&at=11lsTn" iPhone
      '  or
      a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/drafts-for-ipad/id542797283?mt=8&at=11lsTn" iPad
      '). For more information, check out
      a href="http://macstories.net/tutorials/safari-action-menu-in-launch-center-pro/" this article
      ' by Federico Viticci at MacStories.
  .row.news
    .col-xs-12.alert.alert-info
      strong 2014-02-15:
      '  TAKE ACTION now supports
      a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id689989355?mt=8&at=11lsTn" Clear+
      '  and
      a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/pushpin-for-pinboard/id548052590?mt=8&at=11lsTn" Pushpin
      ' .
